      "text_span_id": "disc_1",
      "text": "Mesothelin is one of the widely studied biomarkers of PM, which is expressed at low levels in normal cells and undetectable in normal tissues, but is abundantly expressed in malignant mesothelioma, pancreatic cancer, ovarian cancer, lung cancer, and other cancers",
